1
00:00:33,134 --> 00:00:36,235
I AM SORRY.
UH, PARDON ME. UH--

2
00:00:37,504 --> 00:00:39,270
YOU'RE NAKED.

3
00:00:39,339 --> 00:00:41,506
AND YOU'RE NOT.

4
00:00:41,575 --> 00:00:44,242
UH-UH. NO, I--

5
00:00:44,311 --> 00:00:47,278
<i>SO, EITHER YOU</i>
<i>TAKE YOURS OFF,</i>

6
00:00:47,347 --> 00:00:49,614
<i>OR I'LL PUT MINE ON.</i>

7
00:00:49,683 --> 00:00:53,385
<i> THESE PEOPLE ARE CHASING--</i>
<i> I, UH-- I GOTTA GO.</i>

8
00:00:53,454 --> 00:00:56,755
EASY THERE,
MR. MAINTENANCE MAN.
I WAS JUST RECHARGING MY CORE.

9
00:00:56,824 --> 00:00:59,257
IT'S LIKE TIME TRAVEL
IN<i> THE TERMINATOR.</i>

10
00:00:59,326 --> 00:01:02,027
YOU'VE GOTTA BE IN THE SKIN.
IT'S GREAT FOR YOUR KARMA.

11
00:01:02,095 --> 00:01:04,463
KARMA? WHAT'S KARMA?

12
00:01:04,532 --> 00:01:09,434
UM, EVERY GOOD DEED COMES BACK
TO YOU. LIKE A BOOMERANG,
ONLY YOU DON'T THROW IT.

13
00:01:09,503 --> 00:01:12,937
GOD, YOUR LIFELINE--
IT SAYS YOU'VE BEEN ALONE.

14
00:01:13,006 --> 00:01:15,374
BUT THERE ARE THESE FAMILIES
COMING TOGETHER.

15
00:01:15,442 --> 00:01:18,076
FAMILIES?

16
00:01:18,145 --> 00:01:20,879
WHAT?
THEY'RE LOOKING FOR YOU.

17
00:01:20,948 --> 00:01:24,249
AND WHILE YOU SEARCH FOR THEM,
YOU BRING OTHER
FAMILIES TOGETHER.

18
00:01:24,318 --> 00:01:28,119
KEEP DOING WHAT YOU'RE DOING.
THE GOOD WILL COME BACK.

19
00:01:28,188 --> 00:01:31,623
OH, THANK YOU.
NOW I REALLY HAVE TO GO.

20
00:01:31,692 --> 00:01:36,761
WAIT, YOUR LIFELINE, IT SAID
SOMETHING ELSE. YOU ARE GONNA
MEET SOMEBODY JUST LIKE YOU.

21
00:01:37,731 --> 00:01:40,298
A KINDRED SPIRIT.

22
00:01:40,367 --> 00:01:42,401
A KINDRED SPIRIT. HMM.

23
00:03:24,004 --> 00:03:26,505
UM, MISS,
YOU DROPPED YOUR BAG.

24
00:04:22,896 --> 00:04:24,896
DAMN!

25
00:04:35,676 --> 00:04:37,608
"JENNA."

26
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:52,491
<i>[ Naked Woman's Voice ]</i>
<i>YOU BRING OTHER FAMILIES</i>
<i>TOGETHER.</i>

27
00:04:55,161 --> 00:04:58,296
<i>[ Man Narrating ]</i>
<i>THERE ARE PRETENDERS AMONG US.</i>

28
00:04:58,365 --> 00:05:00,298
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I WAS TAKEN FROM MY FAMILY.</i>

29
00:05:00,367 --> 00:05:03,935
<i>THIRTY-SIX HOURS AND HE'S</i>
<i>ALREADY DEMONSTRATING MORE</i>
<i>TALENT THAN ANY OF OUR OTHERS.</i>

30
00:05:04,004 --> 00:05:07,405
<i>HOW MANY PEOPLE DIED</i>
<i>BECAUSE OF WHAT I THOUGHT UP?</i>

31
00:05:07,474 --> 00:05:10,909
SINCE I BROKE OUT,
I'VE SPENT EVERY MOMENT
SEARCHING FOR MY PAST.

32
00:05:10,978 --> 00:05:13,178
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>HE'S A PRETENDER--</i>

33
00:05:13,247 --> 00:05:16,548
<i>A GENIUS WHO CAN BECOME</i>
<i>ANYONE THAT HE WANTS TO BE.</i>

34
00:05:16,617 --> 00:05:18,816
- THE CENTRE WANTS HIM ALIVE.
- PREFERABLY.

35
00:05:18,885 --> 00:05:21,053
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>HE DEFENDS THE WEAK AND ABUSED.</i>

36
00:05:21,121 --> 00:05:23,788
LIFE'S A GIFT.

37
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:36,267
-<i> YOU A DOCTOR?</i>
- I AM TODAY.

38
00:06:02,229 --> 00:06:04,862
HOW WAS YOUR BREAKFAST,
MR. PRITCHARD?

39
00:06:04,932 --> 00:06:07,498
SAM, YOU MISSED
SOME KILLER PANCAKES.

40
00:06:09,069 --> 00:06:11,937
MY GIRL HERE IS
A BUDDING CHEF.
[ Chuckles ]

41
00:06:12,005 --> 00:06:14,906
WELL, DON'T THANK ME.
THANK BISQUICK.

42
00:06:20,914 --> 00:06:23,181
CHUCK, YOU'RE IN
THE BACK TODAY.

43
00:06:45,172 --> 00:06:48,273
IF ANYBODY NEEDS ME,
I'LL BE PUTTING OUT FIRES.

44
00:06:51,811 --> 00:06:55,513
HERE WE GO. ANOTHER DAY,
ANOTHER DOLLAR.

45
00:06:56,683 --> 00:06:59,951
<i>[ Car Alarm Blaring ]</i>

46
00:07:03,356 --> 00:07:07,191
SOUNDS LIKE THE BUICK.
YEAH, WELL, DOES
NUMB NUTS KNOW?

47
00:07:10,130 --> 00:07:12,263
[ Coughing ]

48
00:07:14,167 --> 00:07:16,734
SECONDHAND SMOKE.
IT'S A KILLER.

49
00:07:16,803 --> 00:07:19,070
[ Ringing ]
YEAH, BABE?

50
00:07:19,139 --> 00:07:21,572
YOU BETTER GET IN HERE.

51
00:07:21,642 --> 00:07:23,441
CHUCK! CHUCK?
<i>[ Chuck ]</i>
<i>SAM! I'M IN THE TRUNK!</i>

52
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:27,378
<i>GET ME OUTTA THE TRUNK!</i>
SON OF A BITCH!

53
00:07:27,447 --> 00:07:31,115
<i>SAM! HURRY UP!</i>
<i>I'M IN THE TRUNK!</i>

54
00:07:32,886 --> 00:07:35,453
- SAM, MEET JAROD GRAY.
- YOU'RE LATE.

55
00:07:35,522 --> 00:07:39,557
- WHAT IS THIS?
- IT'S A TEST. JAROD'S
WITH OUR SECURITY COMPANY.

56
00:07:39,626 --> 00:07:43,795
<i> THE SAME ONE WE'RE PAYING</i>
<i> FOR FOUR-STAR PROTECTION.</i>
<i> THE KIND WE'RE NOT GETTING.</i>

57
00:07:43,863 --> 00:07:46,430
HOW'D YOU BEAT THE CAMERAS?

58
00:07:46,499 --> 00:07:49,734
IT WAS VERY DIFFICULT.
SORRY ABOUT ALL THE BELLS
AND WHISTLES,

59
00:07:49,803 --> 00:07:51,836
BUT THE COMPANY LIKES
TO KEEP OUR MEN FROSTY.

60
00:07:51,904 --> 00:07:55,106
<i>SPEAKING OF WHICH, YOU MIGHT</i>
<i>WANT TO GET YOUR HEAD OF</i>
<i>SECURITY OUT OF THE TRUNK.</i>

61
00:07:55,175 --> 00:07:56,908
IT'S GETTING A LITTLE
CHILLY OUT THERE.

62
00:07:56,977 --> 00:08:00,745
<i>TELL CHUCK, NOW HE'S THE</i>
<i>NIGHT WATCHMAN, AND JAROD'S</i>
<i>THE NEW HEAD OF SECURITY.</i>

63
00:08:00,814 --> 00:08:02,947
<i>GET HIM AN ADVANCE.</i>

64
00:08:03,016 --> 00:08:07,085
ROLAND, THIS ISN'T SMART
RIGHT NOW. WE GOT THAT THING
IN NEW BRUNSWICK.

65
00:08:09,355 --> 00:08:11,822
YOU WANNA BE
THE NIGHT WATCHMAN?

66
00:08:13,827 --> 00:08:16,494
WELCOME ABOARD.

67
00:08:18,098 --> 00:08:20,098
JAROD, DO YOU KNOW JENNA?

68
00:08:21,534 --> 00:08:24,135
YOU LOOK... SO FAMILIAR.

69
00:08:24,204 --> 00:08:27,171
I HAVE ONE OF THOSE FACES.

70
00:08:31,745 --> 00:08:34,245
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>IS MY LITTLE BROTHER</i>
<i>GONNA BE OKAY?</i>

71
00:08:34,314 --> 00:08:40,084
<i> WELL, HIS LUNGS</i>
<i> WERE UNDERDEVELOPED,</i>
<i> BUT THE OXYGEN SHOULD HELP.</i>

72
00:08:40,153 --> 00:08:43,388
THAT'S MY BOY.
GOD'S GREATEST MIRACLE.

73
00:08:43,456 --> 00:08:47,792
[ Speaking Gibberish ]

74
00:08:47,861 --> 00:08:50,729
THE REAL MIRACLE
WOULD BE FOR YOU AND ME...

75
00:08:50,797 --> 00:08:52,864
IN THE SHADOW OF NEW LIFE
TO START ANEW.

76
00:08:52,933 --> 00:08:55,467
THE GOOD BOOK SAYS
"TURN THE OTHER CHEEK."

77
00:08:55,535 --> 00:08:58,302
I ALSO REMEMBER SOMETHING
ABOUT "EYE FOR AN EYE."

78
00:08:58,371 --> 00:09:01,539
<i> OH, JAROD SENT A GIFT.</i>

79
00:09:04,277 --> 00:09:08,913
"CORINTHIANS, 15:25.
EVEN A CHILD
IS KNOWN BY HIS DOINGS."

80
00:09:08,982 --> 00:09:11,749
RING A BELL THERE,
JOHNNY DOGMA?

81
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:17,355
GOD BLESS YOU ALL.
WILLIE, OUR WORK HERE
IS DONE.

82
00:09:17,424 --> 00:09:19,223
<i> [ Sydney ]</i>
<i> IT'S WRONG?</i>

83
00:09:19,292 --> 00:09:21,225
IT'S NOT CORINTHIANS.
IT'S PROVERBS.

84
00:09:21,295 --> 00:09:24,095
OF COURSE RAINES
HAD NO CLUE.
WELL, HOW DID YOU KNOW?

85
00:09:24,164 --> 00:09:26,931
CORINTHIANS, 15:25.

86
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:31,336
"FOR HE MUST REIGN TILL
HE HATH PUT ALL ENEMIES
UNDER HIS FEET."

87
00:09:33,005 --> 00:09:35,606
THE OPERATIVE TERM
BEING "REIGN."

88
00:09:35,675 --> 00:09:38,109
- WHAT DO YOU THINK
JAROD'S TRYING TO TELL US?
- RAINES IS NO CONVERT.

89
00:09:38,178 --> 00:09:40,511
HE ACTUALLY ASKED ME
TO FORGIVE HIM.

90
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:43,181
MAYBE RAINES HAS FOUND GOD.

91
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:46,150
MAYBE HE SHOULD HAVE
THOUGHT OF THAT BEFORE
HE KILLED MY MOTHER.

92
00:09:46,219 --> 00:09:49,187
FIND OUT WHAT THAT
SON OF A BITCH IS UP TO.
OKAY.

93
00:09:55,428 --> 00:09:57,728
<i>[ Sam ]</i>
<i>HEY, LOOK AT THE</i>
<i>NEW GUY HARD AT WORK.</i>

94
00:09:57,797 --> 00:10:00,731
I CALLED THE COMPANY
ABOUT YOU.

95
00:10:00,801 --> 00:10:03,902
I THOUGHT ONLY CUSTOMERS
GOT A BACKGROUND CHECK.

96
00:10:03,970 --> 00:10:05,904
SO, WHAT DID OLD RUDY
HAVE TO SAY?

97
00:10:05,972 --> 00:10:09,573
AH, YOU'RE FROM BALTIMORE,
AN EX-COP.

98
00:10:09,642 --> 00:10:13,077
THAT'S RIGHT.
SIX YEARS HOMICIDE.

99
00:10:13,146 --> 00:10:15,446
I GOT TIRED
OF LOSIN' MY COLLARS
TO THE COURTS.

100
00:10:15,515 --> 00:10:17,648
THAT'S WHERE WE GOTTA
CHANGE THE BOOKS.

101
00:10:17,717 --> 00:10:22,821
2,200 GUN LAWS, MORE THAN
WE CAN ENFORCE, AND I'M
THE BAD GUY? I'M A SALESMAN.

102
00:10:22,889 --> 00:10:26,290
WHY WOULD A COP LEAVE
A FAT PENSION TO TAKE
A BULLET FOR SOMEBODY?

103
00:10:30,931 --> 00:10:33,998
WHY DOES A SALESMAN
NEED TWO BODYGUARDS?

104
00:10:34,067 --> 00:10:36,568
WELL, WE ALL
GOT ENEMIES, JAROD.

105
00:10:36,636 --> 00:10:40,071
WELL, MAYBE YOU SHOULD SPREAD
SOME BETTER KARMA AROUND.

106
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:42,139
KARMA?
YEAH. IT'S LIKE
A BOOMERANG,

107
00:10:42,208 --> 00:10:44,141
ONLY YOU DON'T THROW IT.

108
00:10:46,312 --> 00:10:50,281
- LONG DAY, MRS. PRITCHARD?
- OH, I'M NOT
MRS. PRITCHARD YET.

109
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:54,151
ROLAND'S GOT ME ON LAYAWAY.
WE START MAKIN' WEDDING
PLANS AFTER SATURDAY.

110
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:57,355
- THE TRIP TO NEW BRUNSWICK.
- YEAH. GOTTA SEE A FRIEND.

111
00:10:57,424 --> 00:10:59,858
I'M GONNA WANT THE BUICK SWEPT
AND SECURED TOMORROW MORNING.

112
00:10:59,926 --> 00:11:03,094
<i> GOTTA PROTECT</i>
<i> MY INVESTMENT.</i>

113
00:11:03,163 --> 00:11:06,698
YOU TALKIN' ABOUT ME
OR THE ROCK?
AIN'T I LUCKY?

114
00:11:06,766 --> 00:11:09,467
<i> ALL THIS AND</i>
<i> A SENSE OF HUMOR.</i>

115
00:11:12,238 --> 00:11:14,839
SHE MEANS EVERYTHING TO ME.
YOU TAKE A BULLET FOR HER...

116
00:11:14,907 --> 00:11:17,776
BEFORE YOU EVEN THINK
ABOUT TAKIN' ONE FOR ME.

117
00:11:17,844 --> 00:11:20,445
WELL, I CERTAINLY HOPE
IT DOESN'T COME TO THAT.

118
00:11:31,458 --> 00:11:34,525
<i> [ Car Approaching ]</i>

119
00:11:42,835 --> 00:11:45,136
SHE'S MY DAUGHTER, DENNIS.
I HAVE TO SEE HER.

120
00:11:45,204 --> 00:11:47,305
<i> SHE'S AT ST. CHARLES.</i>

121
00:11:47,374 --> 00:11:51,209
- NO, I'M LEAVING. I'M LEAVING.
- NOT WITHOUT ME, I HOPE.

122
00:11:53,780 --> 00:11:56,580
JAROD.

123
00:11:56,649 --> 00:12:00,985
IT'S ONLY GOING TO GET WORSE
AFTER YOU'RE MARRIED.

124
00:12:01,054 --> 00:12:03,721
HE'S GONNA WANT YOU WATCHED
ALL THE TIME. THEN WHEN
YOU HAVE THE LITTLE ONES--

125
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:06,924
OH, WE WON'T BE
HAVING CHILDREN.

126
00:12:06,993 --> 00:12:09,360
ROLAND'S CHOICE.

127
00:12:09,429 --> 00:12:12,497
- HE'S A GOOD MAN.
- I NEVER SAID HE WASN'T.

128
00:12:12,565 --> 00:12:14,732
YOU THOUGHT IT, THOUGH.

129
00:12:14,801 --> 00:12:17,535
<i>EVERYONE DOES.</i>
<i>IT'S THIS BUSINESS.</i>

130
00:12:17,604 --> 00:12:20,171
<i>BUT ROLAND'S MADE</i>
<i>A GOOD LIFE FOR US.</i>

131
00:12:20,239 --> 00:12:22,173
IT'S LIKE A... HAPPY ENDING.

132
00:12:24,077 --> 00:12:27,211
YOU DO BELIEVE IN
HAPPY ENDINGS, DON'T YOU?

133
00:12:28,415 --> 00:12:31,582
<i>[ Car Approaching ]</i>

134
00:12:36,957 --> 00:12:39,256
GET DOWN!

135
00:12:58,177 --> 00:13:00,177
YOU OKAY?
YEAH.

136
00:13:01,681 --> 00:13:04,315
[ Policeman ]
MAKE A LIST OF ALL
THOSE EMPLOYEES THAT--

137
00:13:04,384 --> 00:13:07,618
I'M SUPPOSED TO KNOW
WHEN YOU LEAVE THE BUILDING.

138
00:13:09,021 --> 00:13:10,955
THANK YOU.

139
00:13:11,023 --> 00:13:14,959
<i>- [ Camera Shutter Clicking ]</i>
- DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHO DID THIS?

140
00:13:15,028 --> 00:13:17,795
I'D RATHER KNOW HOW
THEY GOT SO CLOSE.

141
00:13:17,864 --> 00:13:20,732
- IT WAS MY FAULT.
I JUST-- I WAS--
- NO, IT WAS MY FAULT.

142
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:23,801
<i>I WENT TO GET THE CAR.</i>
<i> I-- I LET MY GUARD DOWN.</i>

143
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:26,270
YOU SAVED HER LIFE.

144
00:13:26,339 --> 00:13:28,940
THAT'S WHAT MATTERS.

145
00:13:29,009 --> 00:13:31,341
SHE'S GONNA HAVE
MY KIDS SOMEDAY.

146
00:13:37,083 --> 00:13:38,982
<i>[ Camera Shutter Clicking ]</i>

147
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:48,660
LET'S GO.

148
00:13:53,033 --> 00:13:55,799
<i>[ Jenna's Voice ]</i>
<i>SHE'S MY DAUGHTER, DENNIS.</i>
<i>I HAVE TO SEE HER.</i>

149
00:13:55,868 --> 00:13:57,801
<i>SHE'S AT ST. CHARLES.</i>

150
00:14:00,874 --> 00:14:03,574
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU, PAL?

151
00:14:10,282 --> 00:14:12,216
THE BODY OF CHRIST.

152
00:14:15,454 --> 00:14:17,888
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

153
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:22,560
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

154
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:25,630
<i>THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

155
00:14:27,266 --> 00:14:29,333
<i>THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

156
00:14:31,404 --> 00:14:34,071
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

157
00:14:34,139 --> 00:14:37,708
<i>THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

158
00:14:37,777 --> 00:14:40,311
THE BODY OF CHRIST.
AMEN.

159
00:14:42,615 --> 00:14:46,083
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i> [ Door Opens ]</i>

160
00:14:46,152 --> 00:14:49,020
<i>THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

161
00:14:49,088 --> 00:14:51,756
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

162
00:14:53,393 --> 00:14:55,325
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>

163
00:14:55,394 --> 00:14:58,028
MR. McGANN, YOUR DAUGHTER
AND I HAVE A DEAL.

164
00:14:58,098 --> 00:15:02,533
<i>SHE'D BETTER HONOR IT</i>
<i>IF SHE KNOWS WHAT'S GOOD</i>
<i>FOR YOU AND THE KID.</i>

165
00:15:02,602 --> 00:15:06,370
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i>[ Door Opens, Closes ]</i>

166
00:15:06,439 --> 00:15:09,540
<i>[ Gunfire ]</i>

167
00:15:18,017 --> 00:15:23,387
UH--
SORRY TO INTERRUPT.
I CAN COME BACK ANOTHER TIME.

168
00:15:23,456 --> 00:15:26,089
NO, UH, I GOT WORK TO DO.

169
00:15:26,158 --> 00:15:28,025
GREAT.

170
00:15:28,093 --> 00:15:32,263
- KEEP AN EYE
ON THE PRIZE, WILL YA?
- OH. SURE, NO PROBLEM.

171
00:15:33,833 --> 00:15:37,134
SO, UH, THANKS AGAIN...
FOR THIS MORNING.

172
00:15:37,203 --> 00:15:39,403
WE'RE REALLY GETTIN'
OUR MONEY'S WORTH.

173
00:15:39,472 --> 00:15:42,940
YOU'RE RIGHT. WE HAVE MET.

174
00:15:44,978 --> 00:15:46,910
AT MY HOUSE.

175
00:15:49,615 --> 00:15:52,416
AGENT DENNIS ALONZO.

176
00:15:52,485 --> 00:15:55,686
HE FOLLOWED ME TO YOUR
DAUGHTER'S FIRST COMMUNION
REHEARSAL AT ST. CHARLES.

177
00:15:55,754 --> 00:15:59,323
HE SEEMS TO BE STRONG-ARMING
YOUR FATHER. WHY?

178
00:15:59,392 --> 00:16:03,260
<i>IS HE TRYING</i>
<i>TO GET YOU TO TESTIFY AGAINST</i>
<i>YOUR FIANCÉ OR SOMETHING?</i>

179
00:16:03,329 --> 00:16:05,996
<i>LOOK, I CAN PROTECT YOU.</i>

180
00:16:06,065 --> 00:16:08,666
AND I CAN HELP YOU
GET YOUR FAMILY BACK.

181
00:16:08,735 --> 00:16:11,635
BUT YOU'RE GOING TO
HAVE TO TRUST ME.

182
00:16:13,672 --> 00:16:16,107
YOU'RE WRONG, MR. GRAY.
I CAN'T TRUST ANYONE.

183
00:16:23,149 --> 00:16:26,450
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE GETTING INTO.

184
00:16:26,518 --> 00:16:31,255
"OPERATION FAT CAT.
OBJECTIVE: SECURE EVIDENCE
ON ROLAND PRITCHARD.

185
00:16:31,324 --> 00:16:34,825
OWNS 10 TRISTATE
GUN SHOPS, MONEY LAUNDERING,
ILLEGAL FILES AND--"

186
00:16:34,893 --> 00:16:37,295
- WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?
- I'M AN EX-COP.

187
00:16:37,363 --> 00:16:39,863
AND I'M SOMEONE
WHO CAN HELP YOU
GET YOUR DAUGHTER BACK.

188
00:16:41,634 --> 00:16:44,402
TELL ME SHE'S OKAY.
ALL RIGHT, I'M GONNA FINISH
THIS ASSIGNMENT.

189
00:16:44,470 --> 00:16:48,906
- JUST TELL ME THAT SHE'S OKAY.
- ASSIGNMENT?

190
00:16:48,975 --> 00:16:52,209
WAIT A MINUTE.
YOU'RE A.T.F.

191
00:16:52,278 --> 00:16:55,780
<i> OH, MY GOD. HOW LONG</i>
<i> HAVE YOU BEEN UNDERCOVER?</i>

192
00:16:58,384 --> 00:17:00,551
TWELVE MONTHS, 13 DAYS.

193
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:04,855
TWELVE MONTHS?
YOU'VE BEEN APART FROM YOUR
DAUGHTER FOR OVER A YEAR?

194
00:17:14,567 --> 00:17:16,500
I MISS MY LITTLE GIRL.

195
00:17:23,576 --> 00:17:26,910
<i>♪♪ [ Rap ]</i>

196
00:17:26,979 --> 00:17:29,546
<i> [ Police Siren Wailing ]</i>

197
00:17:31,618 --> 00:17:33,751
THIS BETTER BE GOOD.
OKAY.

198
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:35,752
THE CARD JAROD
SENT WITH THE GIFT--

199
00:17:35,821 --> 00:17:39,524
THE CHAPTER AND THE
VERSE NUMBERS WERE A CODE
FOR RAINES'S COMPUTER.

200
00:17:39,592 --> 00:17:43,026
EVERY DAY FOR THE LAST
SIX MONTHS, RAINES HAS BEEN
MEETING WITH THAT GUY.

201
00:17:45,998 --> 00:17:48,699
<i> OH, MY GOD.</i>

202
00:17:48,768 --> 00:17:51,736
GIUSEPPE.

203
00:17:51,804 --> 00:17:55,673
<i> YOU KNOW HIM?</i>
JUNIOR YEAR
OF HIGH SCHOOL. ROME.

204
00:17:55,742 --> 00:17:58,075
<i> LOOK AT HIM.</i>

205
00:17:58,144 --> 00:18:00,110
YOU GUYS WERE LIKE
A THING OR SOMETHING?

206
00:18:00,179 --> 00:18:02,846
HE WAS MY DATE
FOR THE SPRING FORMAL.

207
00:18:02,915 --> 00:18:06,350
HE TRIED TO GET TO THIRD BASE
IN THE FRONT SEAT
OF HIS FATHER'S FERRARI.

208
00:18:06,419 --> 00:18:09,186
I BROKE HIS FINGER.

209
00:18:09,255 --> 00:18:11,388
BOY, HE IS
STILL A BISCUIT.

210
00:18:11,457 --> 00:18:13,857
YOU MEAN BISCOTTI,
DON'T YOU?

211
00:18:13,926 --> 00:18:16,159
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>LOOK UP! LOOK UP! LOOK UP!</i>

212
00:18:16,228 --> 00:18:18,195
<i>SHOOT!</i>

213
00:18:22,635 --> 00:18:25,469
<i>♪♪ [ Rap ]</i>

214
00:18:29,108 --> 00:18:31,708
PARKER, IS THAT YOU?

215
00:18:31,777 --> 00:18:34,077
GIUSEPPE.

216
00:18:34,146 --> 00:18:36,413
YOU'RE LOOKING VERY WELL.

217
00:18:36,482 --> 00:18:40,584
YOU TOO. VERY WELL.

218
00:18:42,121 --> 00:18:44,121
GIVE ME A MOMENT,
WILL YA?

219
00:18:44,189 --> 00:18:46,890
HOW'S THE FINGER?

220
00:18:46,959 --> 00:18:51,428
<i>OH, IT'S-- IT'S STILL BENT.</i>

221
00:18:52,498 --> 00:18:54,564
YEAH, I FEEL BAD
ABOUT THAT.

222
00:18:54,633 --> 00:18:58,102
WELL, I HAVE, UH,
CHANGED A LOT SINCE THEN.

223
00:19:02,374 --> 00:19:04,575
YES, YOU HAVE.

224
00:19:12,551 --> 00:19:17,688
THIS ALL STARTED
WHEN WE TRACED SOME GUNS BACK
TO ONE OF ROLAND'S SHOPS.

225
00:19:17,757 --> 00:19:20,757
<i>THEY'D BEEN USED</i>
<i>IN A SCHOOL SHOOTING.</i>

226
00:19:20,827 --> 00:19:25,429
THE OPERATION WAS SUPPOSED
TO TAKE THREE MONTHS, TOPS.

227
00:19:25,497 --> 00:19:27,832
THAT SNOWBALLED INTO A YEAR.

228
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:31,868
<i>I STARTED OUT AS,</i>
<i>UH, ROLAND'S ASSISTANT.</i>

229
00:19:31,937 --> 00:19:34,272
AND THEN ONE DAY
HE ASKED ME OUT.

230
00:19:34,340 --> 00:19:36,640
<i>A.T.F. SAID,</i>
<i>"COULDN'T HURT."</i>

231
00:19:36,709 --> 00:19:39,610
<i>A CUP OF COFFEE</i>
<i>TURNS INTO AN EVENING.</i>

232
00:19:40,813 --> 00:19:43,948
[ Sighs ]
ALONZO FORCED ME
TO GO WITH IT.

233
00:19:44,016 --> 00:19:46,650
<i>THE NEXT THING I KNOW,</i>
<i>I'M WEARING AN ENGAGEMENT RING.</i>

234
00:19:47,953 --> 00:19:50,521
HAVE YOU EVER BEEN
UNDERCOVER, JAROD?

235
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:52,957
ONCE OR TWICE.

236
00:19:59,732 --> 00:20:02,532
SHE HAS YOUR EYES.

237
00:20:06,472 --> 00:20:09,473
YOU'VE SEEN HER?
YES. HER AND
YOUR FATHER.

238
00:20:09,542 --> 00:20:12,008
<i> THEY BOTH LOOK WELL,</i>
<i> CONSIDERING.</i>

239
00:20:12,077 --> 00:20:14,511
<i>HOW LONG HAS IT BEEN</i>
<i>SINCE YOU SAW THEM?</i>

240
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:18,415
TWO MONTHS.
I USED TO GO EVERY WEEK,

241
00:20:18,484 --> 00:20:21,618
BUT, UH, ALONZO PUT
A STOP TO THAT.

242
00:20:21,687 --> 00:20:24,188
SAID ROLAND
WAS GETTING TOO CLOSE.

243
00:20:24,257 --> 00:20:26,991
AND WHAT ABOUT YOU?

244
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:30,328
WERE YOU GETTING TOO CLOSE?

245
00:20:30,396 --> 00:20:32,496
[ Shouting ]
YOU THINK I'M ENJOYING THIS?

246
00:20:32,564 --> 00:20:35,365
<i>LOOK, I KNOW CASSIE NEEDS ME,</i>
<i>BUT I CAN'T WALK!</i>

247
00:20:35,435 --> 00:20:37,835
AND WHAT IF ROLAND
FINDS OUT ABOUT HER?

248
00:20:37,903 --> 00:20:40,871
HER FATHER'S GONE.
SHE CAN'T LOSE
ANOTHER PARENT.

249
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:43,106
JENNA, JUST KEEP
YOUR VOICE DOWN.
I UNDERSTAND.

250
00:20:43,175 --> 00:20:46,209
<i> THEY'VE MOVED CASS</i>
<i> AND MY DAD, AND ALONZO</i>
<i> WON'T LET ME SEE THEM.</i>

251
00:20:46,278 --> 00:20:48,879
<i> WHATEVER IT TAKES</i>
<i> TO GET THE FAT CAT.</i>

252
00:20:48,947 --> 00:20:51,214
DON'T YOU HAVE ENOUGH
ON PRITCHARD TO PUT HIM AWAY?

253
00:20:52,951 --> 00:20:55,119
ROLAND'S NOT THE TARGET.

254
00:20:55,187 --> 00:20:59,824
<i>WE STILL DON'T KNOW WHO</i>
<i>ALL THIS MONEY WASHING'S FOR.</i>
<i>[ Sighs ]</i>

255
00:20:59,892 --> 00:21:03,427
- WE MEET HIM IN TWO DAYS.
- THE OLD FRIEND
IN NEW BRUNSWICK.

256
00:21:03,496 --> 00:21:06,363
DO ME A FAVOR.

257
00:21:06,432 --> 00:21:10,334
KEEP THIS. IT BELONGED
TO MY MOTHER.

258
00:21:10,403 --> 00:21:13,871
I WANT CASSIE TO HAVE
THAT... IF, UH,

259
00:21:13,939 --> 00:21:16,807
THINGS DON'T WORK OUT.

260
00:21:16,875 --> 00:21:18,976
EVERYTHING WILL WORK OUT.

261
00:21:19,045 --> 00:21:22,079
AND THEN WHAT?

262
00:21:24,016 --> 00:21:27,151
I DON'T KNOW WHO
I AM ANYMORE, JAROD.

263
00:21:30,489 --> 00:21:34,258
<i> PEOPLE CHANGE. WE USED</i>
<i> TO CALL YOU "SHIFTY G."</i>

264
00:21:34,327 --> 00:21:36,794
IT'S NO WONDER THAT
YOU'RE RAINES'S PRIEST.

265
00:21:36,862 --> 00:21:38,929
THIS IS ABOUT WILLIAM?

266
00:21:38,998 --> 00:21:41,131
OF COURSE.
JAROD SAID YOU'D COME.

267
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:43,667
YOU KNOW JAROD?

268
00:21:43,736 --> 00:21:46,437
<i>FATHER JAROD IS THE</i>
<i>BISHOP'S FAVORITE ENVOY.</i>

269
00:21:46,505 --> 00:21:49,106
AND MR. RAINES IS STUDYING
TO BE A DEACON.

270
00:21:49,175 --> 00:21:51,408
THAT'S WHY
HE'S MEETING WITH YOU.

271
00:21:51,477 --> 00:21:54,611
NO. DAILY CONFESSION.
WILLIAM LIVES WITH MANY DEMONS.

272
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:56,613
BUT HE IS ALSO
A CHILD OF GOD.

273
00:21:56,682 --> 00:22:01,818
HE WILL BE GRANTED ABSOLUTION...
NO MATTER WHAT HIS SINS.

274
00:22:04,457 --> 00:22:06,523
INCLUDING MURDER?

275
00:22:06,592 --> 00:22:09,826
<i>HE FEELS VERY BADLY</i>
<i>ABOUT CATHERINE'S DEATH,</i>

276
00:22:09,895 --> 00:22:13,163
AND REGRETS PROFOUNDLY
THE PAIN IT CAUSED
HER DAUGHTER.

277
00:22:13,232 --> 00:22:15,632
WHAT OTHER LIES
DID HE TELL YOU?

278
00:22:15,701 --> 00:22:18,335
I CAN'T BETRAY WHAT
HE TOLD ME IN CONFESSION.

279
00:22:18,404 --> 00:22:21,971
HOWEVER, JAROD WAS CURIOUS
ABOUT SOMETHING...

280
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:24,608
MR. RAINES
TOLD HIS ASSOCIATE
IN THE PARKING LOT.

281
00:22:24,677 --> 00:22:27,611
SOMETHING ABOUT
THE... VERITAS PROJECT.

282
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:30,481
<i> VERITAS. TRUTH.</i>

283
00:22:30,549 --> 00:22:35,018
OVERHEARD IN THE PARKING LOT.
IS THAT YOUR WAY
OF BETRAYING A CONFESSION?

284
00:22:35,087 --> 00:22:38,322
I WAS WRONG ABOUT YOU.
YOU'RE WORSE THAN RAINES.

285
00:22:38,391 --> 00:22:41,158
SO FULL OF ANGER.

286
00:22:44,963 --> 00:22:47,030
THAT'S MY RELIGION.

287
00:23:09,555 --> 00:23:12,389
<i>[ Camera Shutter Clicking ]</i>

288
00:23:21,767 --> 00:23:25,002
UH, I'LL BE RIGHT UP.
I'M GONNA MAKE A PHONE CALL.

289
00:23:30,409 --> 00:23:32,943
<i>[ Cell Phone Ringing ]</i>

290
00:23:33,012 --> 00:23:35,212
THIS IS ALONZO.
SO,

291
00:23:36,515 --> 00:23:38,448
HOW DO I LOOK?

292
00:23:40,419 --> 00:23:44,254
SO YOU'RE AN EX-COP,
DETECTIVE JAROD GRAY.
SIX YEARS BALTIMORE P.D.

293
00:23:44,323 --> 00:23:46,790
THAT GIVE YOU SOME RIGHT
TO JEOPARDIZE MY OPERATION?

294
00:23:46,858 --> 00:23:50,694
YOU'RE DOIN' A FINE JOB.
I OVERHEARD JENNA YELLING
AT YOU ON YOUR CELL PHONE.

295
00:23:50,762 --> 00:23:54,097
- YOU'RE LUCKY IT WAS ME THAT
OVERHEARD AND NOT PRITCHARD.
- JEN'S A LITTLE FRAYED NOW.

296
00:23:54,166 --> 00:23:57,133
<i>WHO WOULDN'T BE?</i>
<i>YOU'VE TAKEN HER FAMILY, YOU'RE</i>
<i>PRACTICALLY BLACKMAILING HER.</i>

297
00:23:57,202 --> 00:23:59,236
<i> WHY DON'T YOU ADMIT IT?</i>
<i> YOU'RE IN OVER YOUR HEAD.</i>

298
00:23:59,304 --> 00:24:02,906
YOU THINK I WANTED THIS?
THESE ATTACKS ON PRITCHARD
ARE GETTIN' WORSE.

299
00:24:02,975 --> 00:24:06,276
- I'VE NOTICED.
WHO'S TRYIN' TO KILL HIM?
- YOU TELL ME.

300
00:24:06,345 --> 00:24:09,680
OBVIOUSLY YOU'VE READ MY FILE.
YOU KNOW THAT I WAS A GOOD COP
AND I'M HERE TO HELP.

301
00:24:09,748 --> 00:24:13,650
NOW, WHO IS TRYIN' TO KILL HIM?
<i>THE BEST WE CAN FIGURE</i>
<i>IT'S A CLIENT.</i>

302
00:24:13,719 --> 00:24:15,819
PRITCHARD'S SKIMMING
FROM THE PEOPLE
HE'S LAUNDERING MONEY FOR.

303
00:24:15,888 --> 00:24:18,322
- SO HE'S MORE DANGEROUS
THAN I THOUGHT HE WAS.
- YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

304
00:24:18,391 --> 00:24:20,790
- WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?
- WHO THE HELL ARE YOU, ANYWAY?

305
00:24:20,859 --> 00:24:24,761
I'M SOMEBODY WHO'S TRYING TO
MAKE SURE THAT AGENT McGANN
DOESN'T END UP DEAD.

306
00:24:24,830 --> 00:24:27,364
ABOUT A YEAR AGO,
RIGHT AFTER JEN STARTED
WORKIN' UNDERCOVER HERE,

307
00:24:27,433 --> 00:24:31,234
<i>WE FOUND ONE OF PRITCHARD'S</i>
<i>GUN SUPPLIERS DEAD IN THE</i>
<i>WOODS, DOUBLE TAP AT THE CHEST.</i>

308
00:24:31,303 --> 00:24:34,771
NOW, WORD WAS HE CROSSED
PRITCHARD, BUT WE NEVER FOUND
A WEAPON TO MATCH BALLISTICS.

309
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:37,174
SO, YOU WEREN'T ABLE TO PIN
THE MURDER ON PRITCHARD.

310
00:24:37,242 --> 00:24:39,977
- NO.
- AND NOW YOU'RE HOLDING
AGENT McGANN'S DAUGHTER?

311
00:24:40,046 --> 00:24:42,679
WE'RE NOT HOLDING HER.
WE'RE PROTECTING HER.

312
00:24:42,748 --> 00:24:45,315
<i> BY MAKING HER MOTHER STAY</i>
<i> WITH A KILLER?</i>

313
00:24:45,384 --> 00:24:48,085
JEN MAY BE IN DEEP,
BUT SHE'S THE BEST AGENT I KNOW.

314
00:24:48,153 --> 00:24:52,289
- THREE MORE DAYS,
SHE'LL GET US WHAT WE NEED.
- US... OR YOU?

315
00:25:16,448 --> 00:25:18,381
EXCUSE ME, MR. McGANN?

316
00:25:20,786 --> 00:25:23,287
AGENT JAROD GRAY,
A.T.F.

317
00:25:23,355 --> 00:25:27,123
I CAME DOWN HERE
TO TELL YOU THAT YOUR DAUGHTER
WILL BE HOME SOON.

318
00:25:27,192 --> 00:25:30,861
JUST IN TIME FOR CASSIE'S
FIRST COMMUNION, RIGHT?

319
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:33,964
I DON'T BELIEVE
A.T.F. LIES ANYMORE.

320
00:25:34,032 --> 00:25:36,967
THAT'S NOT A LIE, SIR.
IT'S A PROMISE.

321
00:25:39,638 --> 00:25:43,540
CASSIE. MR. GRAY HERE WORKS
WITH YOUR MOTHER.

322
00:25:44,943 --> 00:25:47,010
MY MOMMY CATCHES BAD GUYS.

323
00:25:47,079 --> 00:25:51,849
YES, CASSIE, SHE DOES.
SHE ASKED ME TO
COME DOWN HERE...

324
00:25:51,917 --> 00:25:55,718
TO TELL YOU THAT
SHE MISSES YOU VERY MUCH,
AND SHE'LL SEE YOU SOON.

325
00:25:57,823 --> 00:26:00,590
I SEE HER AT NIGHT,
IN MY DREAMS.

326
00:26:00,659 --> 00:26:02,559
BUT IT'S NOT THE SAME.

327
00:26:05,231 --> 00:26:09,299
CASSIE, YOUR MOM ASKED ME
TO GIVE YOU THIS.

328
00:26:09,368 --> 00:26:12,402
SHE WANTS YOU TO
TAKE VERY GOOD CARE OF IT.

329
00:26:12,471 --> 00:26:16,773
<i>LOOK AT THAT, KIDDO.</i>
<i>THAT WAS YOUR GRANDMA'S RING.</i>

330
00:26:18,276 --> 00:26:21,278
MOMMY HASN'T COME
IN A LONG TIME.

331
00:26:21,347 --> 00:26:23,280
DOES SHE NOT WANNA
SEE US?

332
00:26:23,349 --> 00:26:26,049
OF COURSE SHE DOES, CASSIE.

333
00:26:30,789 --> 00:26:32,923
I TELL YOU WHAT.

334
00:26:32,992 --> 00:26:36,894
YOU SAVE A SEAT FOR HER
AT YOUR COMMUNION.

335
00:26:38,597 --> 00:26:41,732
<i> THAT'S A MIGHTY BIG PROMISE</i>
<i> YOU'RE MAKING.</i>

336
00:26:44,103 --> 00:26:46,937
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>SHE'LL BE HERE.</i>

337
00:27:05,490 --> 00:27:07,924
<i>[ Gunfire ]</i>

338
00:27:24,042 --> 00:27:26,009
<i>JENNA, PRITCHARD, GET DOWN!</i>

339
00:27:26,078 --> 00:27:28,612
[ Gunshot ]

340
00:27:51,003 --> 00:27:53,169
<i>[ Footsteps Approaching ]</i>

341
00:27:54,672 --> 00:27:57,941
STRIKE ME DOWN NOW, LORD.

342
00:28:02,681 --> 00:28:05,682
WILLIE.

343
00:28:08,954 --> 00:28:11,521
MISS PARKER.

344
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:15,692
THIS SAINTLY ROUTINE
IS WEARIN' KIND OF THIN,
DON'T YOU THINK, DEACON?

345
00:28:15,761 --> 00:28:18,128
YOU'VE BEEN TALKING
TO MY PRIEST.

346
00:28:21,032 --> 00:28:23,566
PLEASE. SIT.

347
00:28:29,875 --> 00:28:34,711
WE'VE BEEN DOWN
A DARK ROAD, YOU AND I.
OUR FOOTPRINTS SIDE-BY-SIDE.

348
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:36,913
BUT AT TIMES...

349
00:28:38,517 --> 00:28:41,518
<i>THERE WAS ONLY ONE SET.</i>

350
00:28:41,586 --> 00:28:44,220
THAT WAS WHEN I CARRIED YOU.

351
00:28:44,289 --> 00:28:46,355
REALLY?

352
00:28:46,424 --> 00:28:49,559
I THOUGHT THAT WAS WHEN
YOU WERE OFF KILLING MY MOTHER.

353
00:28:51,163 --> 00:28:54,364
BELIEVE WHAT YOU MUST BELIEVE,
MISS PARKER.

354
00:28:54,433 --> 00:28:57,434
BUT FIND IT IN YOUR HEART
TO FORGIVE ME. IT WILL
GIVE YOU INNER PEACE.

355
00:28:57,502 --> 00:29:00,003
<i>[ Cell Phone Ringing ]</i>

356
00:29:01,506 --> 00:29:03,272
WHAT?

357
00:29:03,341 --> 00:29:06,075
- WHERE ARE YOU?
- YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE ME
IF I TOLD YOU.

358
00:29:06,144 --> 00:29:08,444
THIS VERITAS THING
RAINES AND WILLIE
WERE TALKING ABOUT.

359
00:29:08,513 --> 00:29:11,381
IT'S AN EXPERIMENTAL
AIRBORNE TOXIN...

360
00:29:11,450 --> 00:29:14,551
<i>DEVELOPED BY THE CENTRE</i>
<i>AND SHELVED IN THE '80s.</i>

361
00:29:14,620 --> 00:29:18,120
- RAINES IS RESURRECTING IT.
- SOME PEOPLE CAN'T RESIST
TEMPTATION.

362
00:29:22,861 --> 00:29:26,295
YOU KNOW THE ONE ABOUT
"THOU SHALL NOT COVET"?
OF COURSE.

363
00:29:26,364 --> 00:29:28,598
THAT'S ONE COMMANDMENT
YOU DON'T WANT TO BREAK.

364
00:29:36,508 --> 00:29:40,777
THANKING YOU IS GETTIN'
TO BE A HABIT.
JUST DOING MY JOB.

365
00:29:40,845 --> 00:29:44,414
- WHAT'S THE WORD ON THE GUNMAN?
-<i> MURETTA AND I GOTTA</i>
<i>  TALK TO THE COPS.</i>

366
00:29:44,483 --> 00:29:47,784
YOU OKAY?

367
00:29:59,231 --> 00:30:02,899
THAT LOOK IN YOUR EYES,
IT'S GENUINE CONCERN FOR HIM.

368
00:30:04,803 --> 00:30:06,969
EMOTIONAL ASSIMILATION.

369
00:30:07,038 --> 00:30:10,773
THE PSYCHOLOGICAL
SIDE EFFECT OF PROLONGED
UNDERCOVER WORK.

370
00:30:10,842 --> 00:30:13,376
YOU ARE AN EXPERT.

371
00:30:15,547 --> 00:30:19,315
<i>JUST DON'T FORGET THAT THE MAN</i>
<i>YOU'RE ENGAGED TO IS A KILLER.</i>

372
00:30:19,384 --> 00:30:23,019
ROLAND'S DONE A LOT
OF TERRIBLE THINGS,
BUT HE'S NO KILLER.

373
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:27,356
- ALONZO DIDN'T TELL YOU,
DID HE?
- TELL ME WHAT?

374
00:30:27,425 --> 00:30:29,859
HE'S UNBELIEVABLE.

375
00:30:29,928 --> 00:30:33,329
JAROD?

376
00:30:33,398 --> 00:30:35,798
ALONZO HAS LEFT OUT
A SMALL DETAIL.

377
00:30:35,868 --> 00:30:39,335
SINCE HE PUT THAT RING
ON YOUR FINGER, PRITCHARD
KILLED A GUN SUPPLIER.

378
00:30:39,404 --> 00:30:44,874
WHAT?
STAY FOCUSED OR GET OUT.

379
00:30:44,943 --> 00:30:48,244
OKAY, UH--

380
00:30:48,313 --> 00:30:50,780
LET'S JUST SAY
THAT HE IS A KILLER.

381
00:30:50,848 --> 00:30:53,716
THAT'S ALL THE MORE REASON
FOR ME TO STAY UNDER.

382
00:30:53,786 --> 00:30:57,520
I DON'T WANT ANYTHING TO
HAPPEN TO MY LITTLE GIRL.

383
00:30:57,589 --> 00:30:59,556
IT'S JUST...

384
00:31:01,559 --> 00:31:05,128
ONE MORE NIGHT,
UNLESS, OF COURSE,
YOU KNOW...

385
00:31:05,196 --> 00:31:08,564
WHERE THE MEETING IS
IN NEW BRUNSWICK.

386
00:31:08,633 --> 00:31:11,467
YOUR FIANCÉ KEEPS THAT
A SECRET.

387
00:31:11,536 --> 00:31:14,470
<i>THEN AGAIN, I KNOW</i>
<i>WHERE HE KEEPS THOSE.</i>

388
00:31:29,254 --> 00:31:31,154
[ Beeps ]

389
00:31:34,459 --> 00:31:36,826
[ Beeps ]

390
00:31:38,497 --> 00:31:41,031
[ Beeps ]

391
00:31:41,099 --> 00:31:44,233
[ Beeping ]

392
00:32:05,357 --> 00:32:08,057
<i> LOOKS LIKE</i>
<i> YOUR COVER'S BLOWN,</i>
<i> AGENT McGANN.</i>

393
00:32:20,772 --> 00:32:22,872
THIS IS WHAT RAINES
WAS UP TO.

394
00:32:22,941 --> 00:32:26,309
VERITAS WAS TESTED HERE
IN THE EARLY '80s.

395
00:32:26,377 --> 00:32:30,880
IF THIS IS A DEAD END, I'M GONNA
TRACK DOWN FATHER GIUSEPPE
AND BREAK HIS OTHER NINE DIGITS.

396
00:32:30,949 --> 00:32:32,882
IT MIGHT BE KIND OF FUN,
ACTUALLY.

397
00:32:32,951 --> 00:32:37,487
MORE OF THAT FORBIDDEN
PRIEST THING, HUH?
[ Chuckles ] JUST OPEN THE DOOR.

398
00:32:38,723 --> 00:32:41,224
THE DOOR SEEMS TO BE
PRESSURIZED OR SOMETHING.

399
00:32:41,292 --> 00:32:43,959
I GOT IT.

400
00:32:48,366 --> 00:32:51,066
[ Coughs ]
THERE'S SOME KIND OF GAS!

401
00:32:53,871 --> 00:32:57,740
<i>BROOTS! BROOTS!</i>
<i>OH, MY GOD!</i>
<i>BROOTS! BROOTS!</i>

402
00:32:57,809 --> 00:33:01,344
[ Coughs ]
CANARY. CANARY IN
A COAL MINE. CANARY.

403
00:33:01,413 --> 00:33:03,346
CANARY IN A COAL MINE?

404
00:33:03,414 --> 00:33:05,348
[ Coughing Continues ]

405
00:33:05,417 --> 00:33:09,919
BROOTS, I WANT YOU TO FIND OUT
ANYTHING ELSE YOU CAN ABOUT HOW
THIS GAS COULD POSSIBLY BE USED.

406
00:33:09,987 --> 00:33:14,491
I'M GONNA GO FIND
FATHER GIUSEPPE.
HAVE SYDNEY TAKE A LOOK AT YOU.

407
00:33:14,559 --> 00:33:17,427
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL HER?
CERTAIN DETAILS ARE KEPT
FROM AN AGENT.

408
00:33:17,495 --> 00:33:19,929
STOP MAKING EXCUSES.
YOU CROSSED THE LINE.

409
00:33:19,997 --> 00:33:22,432
THE MAN IS A KILLER!
THE AGENT
COULD BE COMPROMISED!

410
00:33:22,500 --> 00:33:25,501
THE AGENT WAS COMPROMISED!
WHAT?

411
00:33:25,570 --> 00:33:27,604
I FOUND JENNA'S PERSONNEL FILE
IN PRITCHARD'S GUN SAFE.

412
00:33:27,672 --> 00:33:29,839
LISTEN TO ME.
WE DON'T MAKE A MOVE UNTIL
PRITCHARD MAKES A MOVE.

413
00:33:29,907 --> 00:33:34,010
WHAT IF HE MAKES A MOVE ON
JENNA? YOU PREPARED TO DREDGE
YOUR AGENT UP FROM THE HUDSON?

414
00:33:34,078 --> 00:33:36,011
SHE KNOWS THE RISKS.
WHAT DID YOU JUST SAY?

415
00:33:36,081 --> 00:33:39,749
IT'S THE JOB!
IS MAKING HER DAUGHTER AN ORPHAN
PART OF THE JOB TOO?

416
00:33:39,817 --> 00:33:42,518
WE'LL WATCH PRITCHARD.
HE WON'T TAKE A DUMP WITHOUT US
KNOWING. HE WON'T DO ANYTHING.

417
00:33:42,587 --> 00:33:44,621
YOU'D BETTER PRAY
THAT HE DOESN'T.

418
00:33:47,158 --> 00:33:49,892
YOU'RE THE BODYGUARD!
PROTECT HER!

419
00:33:54,633 --> 00:33:57,299
<i>THOSE MANDATORY TRIGGER LOCKS,</i>
<i>THEY'RE A BITCH,</i>
<i>AREN'T THEY?</i>

420
00:33:57,368 --> 00:34:00,069
THEY'RE NOT MANDATORY YET.

421
00:34:00,138 --> 00:34:03,773
I GOT NO ILLUSIONS
ABOUT WHAT I DO, JAROD.

422
00:34:03,842 --> 00:34:06,743
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHIN'.
WHEN SOME PISSED-OFF
DAY TRADER...

423
00:34:06,811 --> 00:34:08,878
DECIDES TO TAKE AN A.K.
TO HIS BROKERAGE FIRM,

424
00:34:08,947 --> 00:34:11,580
I'M NOT STANDIN' THERE
HANDIN' HIM BULLETS
EITHER.

425
00:34:11,650 --> 00:34:14,116
BUT WHAT IF HE NEEDS
SOME MONEY LAUNDERED?

426
00:34:14,185 --> 00:34:16,052
COME AGAIN?

427
00:34:16,120 --> 00:34:19,322
I LIKE TO KNOW
WHO I'M PROTECTING.

428
00:34:20,892 --> 00:34:23,359
SOMETIMES KNOWLEDGE
IS NOT POWER.

429
00:34:23,428 --> 00:34:26,829
WELL, IN MY CASE, IT IS.

430
00:34:26,898 --> 00:34:30,199
JENNA ISN'T EXACTLY
WHO SHE SAYS SHE IS.

431
00:34:30,268 --> 00:34:32,235
SHE'S A.T.F.

432
00:34:36,741 --> 00:34:40,109
WHO HAVE YOU TOLD
ABOUT THIS?
NOBODY.

433
00:34:40,178 --> 00:34:44,580
LOOKS LIKE NOW YOU'RE GONNA
NEED SOME HELP CALLING OFF
YOUR ENGAGEMENT.

434
00:34:44,649 --> 00:34:47,684
LET'S JUST SAY
I HAVE SOME EXPERIENCE
IN THIS ARENA.

435
00:34:47,752 --> 00:34:51,254
NO. I MEANT WHAT
I SAID. YOU TAKE
A BULLET FOR HER.

436
00:34:51,322 --> 00:34:55,825
-<i> JEN IS MY FUTURE.</i>
- ARE YOU TELLIN' ME
YOU'RE IN LOVE WITH HER?

437
00:34:55,894 --> 00:35:00,363
LET'S JUST SAY I'M IN LOVE
WITH WHAT SHE CAN GIVE ME--
A GET-OUT-OF-JAIL-FREE CARD.

438
00:35:00,431 --> 00:35:04,934
SO, TONIGHT, WHEN WE'RE SAFE,
JENNA RADIOS HER BOSS
AND I GIVE THEM THE FAT CAT...

439
00:35:05,002 --> 00:35:10,005
AND WE GET A LITTLE
BEACH HOUSE IN A SEXY,
NON-EXTRADITION COUNTRY.

440
00:35:10,074 --> 00:35:12,474
- IF SHE FOLLOWS THE PLAN.
- SHE WILL.

441
00:35:12,543 --> 00:35:17,547
A COLT 1911 "A."
IT CAN BE VERY CONVINCING.

442
00:35:17,615 --> 00:35:20,482
BUT I GOT SOMETHIN'
BETTER THAN THAT.

443
00:35:20,551 --> 00:35:23,018
JEN'S DAUGHTER.
CUTE KID, HUH?

444
00:35:23,087 --> 00:35:27,690
LIKE I SAID, JAROD,
I GOT NO ILLUSIONS
ABOUT WHAT I DO.

445
00:35:38,436 --> 00:35:40,804
<i>[ Giuseppe ]</i>
<i>YOU KNOW HOW I STAND ON THIS.</i>

446
00:35:40,872 --> 00:35:43,873
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>RAINES TOLD ME WHAT HE'S</i>
<i>DOING WITH THE VERITAS GAS.</i>

447
00:35:43,942 --> 00:35:46,609
HE CONFESSED!
HE SAID NOTHING ABOUT THAT.

448
00:35:46,678 --> 00:35:50,313
HE'S A PSYCHOTIC KILLER.
AND HE'S UP
TO SOMETHING HORRIFIC.

449
00:35:50,381 --> 00:35:53,049
DO YOU DEFINE ALL MEN
BY THEIR SINS?
ONLY THE BAD ONES.

450
00:35:53,117 --> 00:35:58,020
ONLY THE ONES THAT TAKE
A GIRL IN THE BASILICA
DE ROMA AND COP A FEEL.

451
00:35:58,090 --> 00:36:01,791
THAT'S NOT TRUE AND YOU KNOW IT.
THIS ISN'T ABOUT TWO TEENAGERS
GROPING IN A BASILICA.

452
00:36:01,859 --> 00:36:04,927
BESIDES, IT WAS YOU
WHO CAME ON TO ME.
[ Scoffs ]

453
00:36:04,995 --> 00:36:07,596
I REJECTED YOU. THE PAIN OF THAT
REJECTION LIVES INSIDE YOU.
NOT TRUE.

454
00:36:07,666 --> 00:36:10,166
IT IS TRUE, PARKER.
YOU'VE REWRITTEN HISTORY.

455
00:36:10,234 --> 00:36:13,369
CREATE AN ENEMY IN YOUR MIND
BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT
YOU NEEDED TO SURVIVE.

456
00:36:13,438 --> 00:36:16,071
ANGER IS YOUR RELIGION.

457
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:21,010
AND YOU NEED ENEMIES LIKE ME
AND MR. RAINES TO FUEL
THAT DISTORTED FAITH.

458
00:36:21,078 --> 00:36:23,413
IF THY BROTHER TRESPASS
AGAINST YOU, REBUKE HIM.

459
00:36:23,481 --> 00:36:26,616
<i>AND IF HE REPENT,</i>
<i>FORGIVE HIM.</i>

460
00:36:26,684 --> 00:36:31,186
- HE KILLED MY MOTHER.
- IF HE TRESPASSED
AGAINST THEE...

461
00:36:31,255 --> 00:36:34,523
- HE HAS PRESIDED OVER EVERY
MOMENT OF PAIN IN MY LIFE.
- SEVEN TIMES IN A DAY,

462
00:36:34,592 --> 00:36:37,026
HE'S A MONSTER!
THOU SHALT FORGIVE HIM!

463
00:36:37,095 --> 00:36:40,896
AND YOU ARE NOT HIS PRIEST.
YOU'RE HIS COCONSPIRATOR!

464
00:36:42,133 --> 00:36:44,200
FORGIVE YOURSELF, PARKER.

465
00:36:44,269 --> 00:36:48,737
IF YOU DON'T, YOU'LL SURELY
BE DAMMED TO A LIFE
OF ETERNAL SUFFERING.

466
00:36:53,278 --> 00:36:55,878
GOD FORGIVES.

467
00:36:55,946 --> 00:36:57,946
I DON'T.

468
00:37:08,259 --> 00:37:11,260
<i>[ Bell Tolling ]</i>

469
00:37:11,329 --> 00:37:13,329
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>YOU CAN'T PUT YOUR FAITH</i>
<i>IN HIM.</i>

470
00:37:13,398 --> 00:37:16,064
HE WOULDN'T HURT HER.
YOU CAN'T TAKE THAT CHANCE.

471
00:37:16,133 --> 00:37:19,802
I DON'T HAVE A CHOICE!
I HAVE TO GO WITH HIM TONIGHT.
JEN, LISTEN TO--

472
00:37:19,870 --> 00:37:21,771
NO. I HAVE TO
FINISH THIS...

473
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:24,006
AND KNOW
THAT SON OF A BITCH
IS BEHIND BARS.

474
00:37:24,074 --> 00:37:26,241
IT'S THE ONLY WAY THAT
CASSIE CAN BE SAFE.

475
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:29,745
<i> YOU CAN'T TALK ME</i>
<i> OUT OF THIS.</i>

476
00:37:43,127 --> 00:37:45,294
WHERE'S JAROD?
I SENT HIM HOME.

477
00:37:45,363 --> 00:37:47,930
WHY?

478
00:37:47,999 --> 00:37:51,433
ROLL, BABY.

479
00:37:51,503 --> 00:37:53,435
I GOT A CONFESSION
TO MAKE.

480
00:37:55,373 --> 00:37:59,842
<i> JEN! YOU HAVE TO TRUST ME.</i>
<i> DON'T DO THIS.</i>

481
00:37:59,911 --> 00:38:02,412
ALL RIGHT, SOMEBODY TELL ME
WHAT THE HELL IS GOIN' ON.

482
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:04,847
- I KNOW YOU KNOW WHO I AM.
- DON'T TELL HIM ANYTHING!

483
00:38:04,916 --> 00:38:07,549
STOP! I'LL DO WHAT YOU ASK.

484
00:38:07,618 --> 00:38:10,987
<i>I'LL HELP YOU OUT</i>
<i>OF THE COUNTRY.</i>
<i>JUST DON'T HURT MY DAUGHTER.</i>

485
00:38:11,055 --> 00:38:14,057
- DON'T GO WITH HIM.
- SHUT UP! YOU BACK OFF.

486
00:38:14,125 --> 00:38:18,027
NO MATTER WHAT HE SAYS, YOU
CAN'T BELIEVE HIM! HE'S STILL
GOING TO KILL YOUR DAUGHTER!

487
00:38:18,095 --> 00:38:20,129
I WOULD NEVER KILL
A LITTLE GIRL.

488
00:38:20,197 --> 00:38:22,198
[ Gasping ]

489
00:38:22,266 --> 00:38:25,167
[ Groaning ]

490
00:38:28,573 --> 00:38:30,406
JAROD, I'M SORRY.

491
00:38:43,687 --> 00:38:46,489
GET IN THE CAR.

492
00:38:46,558 --> 00:38:48,657
YOU KNOW WHAT.
IT'S FUNNY.

493
00:38:48,726 --> 00:38:52,528
BUT I ACTUALLY DID
FALL IN LOVE WITH YOU,
IN A STRANGE WAY.

494
00:38:52,597 --> 00:38:54,630
THEN YOU HAD TO
TEAR MY HEART OUT.

495
00:38:54,698 --> 00:38:56,966
BUT I GUESS YOU MADE
THE RIGHT CHOICE.

496
00:38:57,035 --> 00:38:59,134
OH, SHE DID.

497
00:39:00,204 --> 00:39:01,804
YOU MISSED ME!

498
00:39:05,610 --> 00:39:08,845
YOU KNOW, I HEARD THIS SONG ONCE
THAT HAPPINESS WAS A WARM GUN.

499
00:39:08,913 --> 00:39:10,846
YES, IT IS.

500
00:39:10,915 --> 00:39:13,582
<i>YOU NEED</i>
<i>A COOLING-DOWN PERIOD.</i>

501
00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:17,654
[ Grunting ]

502
00:39:34,305 --> 00:39:38,440
SHOOTING AN EX-COP.
NOT A VERY SMART IDEA.

503
00:39:38,509 --> 00:39:41,143
<i>ESPECIALLY WHEN HE'S PUT</i>
<i>BLANKS IN YOUR CLIP.</i>

504
00:39:41,212 --> 00:39:44,380
<i>YOU SEE,</i>
<i>THERE'S THIS OPEN CASE</i>
<i>OVER AT THE A.T.F.</i>

505
00:39:44,449 --> 00:39:48,117
SOMETHING ABOUT A GUN SUPPLIER
FOUND SHOT TO DEATH
IN THE WOODS.

506
00:39:48,186 --> 00:39:50,886
<i>THEY NEVER COULD MAKE</i>
<i>A BALLISTICS MATCH.</i>

507
00:39:50,955 --> 00:39:54,190
OR FIND THE KILLER.
NOW THEY WILL.

508
00:39:54,259 --> 00:39:56,959
<i>[ Jenna ]</i>
<i>WANT TO KNOW</i>
<i>SOMETHING FUNNY?</i>

509
00:39:57,028 --> 00:40:00,696
I HAD FEELINGS FOR YOU.
BUT YOU HAD TO GO...

510
00:40:00,765 --> 00:40:03,065
AND THREATEN MY LITTLE GIRL.

511
00:40:03,134 --> 00:40:05,835
BAD DECISION.

512
00:40:05,903 --> 00:40:09,705
<i>KARMA. AIN'T IT A BITCH?</i>

513
00:40:14,445 --> 00:40:17,546
THIS IS ALONZO. OVER.
[ Jarod Over Radio ]
ALONZO.

514
00:40:17,615 --> 00:40:21,583
JAROD, YOU BASTARD,
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE WITH JENNA?
SHE'S SAFE AND SOUND.

515
00:40:21,652 --> 00:40:24,420
NOW, DID YOU EVER
GET THE FAT CAT?
WE GOT HIM.

516
00:40:24,489 --> 00:40:28,724
- BUT NO PRITCHARD.
- CHECK THE THIRD ALLEY
OFF OF 18th STREET.

517
00:40:28,793 --> 00:40:32,761
OH, AND, UH, I LEFT
A LITTLE PRESENT FOR YOU
UNDER YOUR SEAT.

518
00:40:41,972 --> 00:40:45,607
<i>[ Broots ] WE TRACKED DOWN SOME</i>
<i>OF THE PROPERTIES OF THE GAS</i>
<i>THAT RAINES WAS DEVELOPING.</i>

519
00:40:45,676 --> 00:40:50,779
VERITAS RELAXES THE LUNGS
TO THE POINT WHERE THEY CAN
NO LONGER TAKE IN OXYGEN.

520
00:40:50,848 --> 00:40:52,915
IN SMALL DOSES,
IT'S NOT EVEN LETHAL.

521
00:40:52,984 --> 00:40:54,917
I'M SURE RAINES
SKIPPED THAT PART.

522
00:40:54,986 --> 00:40:58,687
<i>WEAK LUNGS IS ONE OF</i>
<i>THE THEORIES BEHIND SUDDEN</i>
<i>INFANT DEATH SYNDROME.</i>

523
00:40:58,756 --> 00:41:01,591
OH, MY GOD. THE BABY.

524
00:41:05,864 --> 00:41:09,665
[ Speaking Gibberish ]

525
00:41:09,734 --> 00:41:12,435
<i> STOP!</i>
<i> GET AWAY FROM HIM!</i>

526
00:41:14,739 --> 00:41:16,972
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE UP TO
WITH THE VERITAS.

527
00:41:17,041 --> 00:41:22,511
I DON'T THINK YOU DO. A DILUTED
VERSION OF VERITAS GAS HELPED ME
LOOSEN BABY PARKER'S LUNGS.

528
00:41:22,580 --> 00:41:25,815
[ Fussing ]

529
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:31,887
HE'S FREE OF
THIS BALL AND CHAIN.

530
00:41:31,956 --> 00:41:35,357
I WISH I COULD SAY
THE SAME FOR MYSELF.

531
00:41:35,426 --> 00:41:37,993
I SAW THE TESTING ROOM.

532
00:41:38,062 --> 00:41:40,296
THERE ARE MANY VILLAINS
IN THE CENTRE, MISS PARKER.

533
00:41:40,365 --> 00:41:42,732
<i>I KNOW YOU NEED THEM</i>
<i>TO SURVIVE.</i>

534
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:45,635
BUT I CAN'T BE
YOUR ENEMY ANYMORE.

535
00:42:06,691 --> 00:42:10,659
<i>[ Priest ] THIS IS THE LAMB</i>
<i>OF GOD WHO TAKES AWAY</i>
<i>THE SINS OF THE WORLD.</i>

536
00:42:10,728 --> 00:42:13,962
HAPPY ARE WE WHO ARE CALLED
TO THE LORD'S SUPPER.

537
00:42:30,314 --> 00:42:33,282
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i> [ Girl ]</i>
<i> AMEN.</i>

538
00:42:33,351 --> 00:42:37,086
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i> [ Girl #2 ]</i>
<i> AMEN.</i>

539
00:42:37,155 --> 00:42:39,087
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i> [ Girl #3 ]</i>
<i> AMEN.</i>

540
00:42:39,156 --> 00:42:43,425
-<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
- AMEN.

541
00:42:45,997 --> 00:42:49,264
<i> THE BODY OF CHRIST.</i>
<i> [ Girl #4 ]</i>
<i> AMEN.</i>

542
00:42:51,902 --> 00:42:54,369
<i> MAY ALMIGHTY GOD BLESS YOU,</i>
<i> THE FATHER,</i>

543
00:42:54,438 --> 00:42:57,139
<i> THE SON,</i>
<i> AND THE HOLY SPIRIT.</i>

544
00:42:57,208 --> 00:43:02,244
<i>THE MASS HAS ENDED. LET US GO</i>
<i>IN PEACE TO ALWAYS LOVE</i>
<i>AND SERVE THE LORD.</i>

545
00:43:10,621 --> 00:43:13,288
LOOK AT YOUR MOTHER.

546
00:43:13,357 --> 00:43:17,359
YOU GOT THE BAD GUY?
WE GOT HIM.
NOW LET'S GO HOME.

